dct_title_s: Map of the Province of La Rĩoja, shewing the routes of Messrs. French, Gosselman & Hibbert
dct_description_sm: Routes of French (1826), Hibbert (1821), and Gosselman (1837) are labeled by dates. Relief shown by hachures. Linear scales show English miles and Spanish leagues. From: Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 9 (1839), pp. 381-408; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v.9 1839
dct_publisher_sm: London : published for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society, by J. Murray, Albemarle Street, 1839.
